evaluatorContext.idealResponse:
Design an API integration for Slack notifications:

INTEGRATION: Slack Notification on Urgent Ticket

---

TRIGGER CONDITION:
```json
{
  "trigger": "ticket_classified",
  "conditions": [
    {"field": "priority", "operator": "equals", "value": "urgent"},
    {"field": "category", "operator": "in", "value": ["outage", "security", "data_loss"]}
  ]
}
```

---

AI OUTPUT (from classifier):
```json
{
  "ticket_id": "TKT-12345",
  "subject": "Production database down",
  "priority": "urgent",
  "category": "outage",
  "customer": "Acme Corp",
  "customer_tier": "enterprise",
  "summary": "Customer reports complete database outage affecting all users",
  "recommended_action": "Immediate escalation to on-call engineer"
}
```

---

API PAYLOAD GENERATION PROMPT:

```
Generate a Slack API payload for this urgent ticket notification.

Ticket data:
{{ai_classifier_output}}

Slack API Requirements:
- Endpoint: POST https://slack.com/api/chat.postMessage
- Content-Type: application/json
- Authorization: Bearer {{SLACK_BOT_TOKEN}}

Required payload schema:
{
  "channel": "string (channel ID)",
  "text": "string (fallback text)",
  "attachments": [
    {
      "color": "string (hex color)",
      "title": "string",
      "text": "string",
      "fields": [
        {"title": "string", "value": "string", "short": boolean}
      ],
      "actions": [
        {"type": "button", "text": "string", "url": "string", "style": "string"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

Mapping rules:
- channel: Use #urgent-support for priority=urgent, else #support-tickets
- color: "#FF0000" for urgent, "#FFA500" for high, "#36A64F" for normal
- Include ticket ID, customer, category, summary in fields
- Add "View Ticket" button linking to ticket URL
- Add "Acknowledge" button for on-call response

Return ONLY the JSON payload.
```

---

EXPECTED OUTPUT:
```json
{
  "channel": "C0123URGENT",
  "text": "[URGENT] TKT-12345: Production database down - Acme Corp",
  "attachments": [
    {
      "color": "#FF0000",
      "title": "URGENT: Production database down",
      "title_link": "https://support.example.com/tickets/TKT-12345",
      "text": "Customer reports complete database outage affecting all users",
      "fields": [
        {
          "title": "Ticket ID",
          "value": "TKT-12345",
          "short": true
        },
        {
          "title": "Customer",
          "value": "Acme Corp (Enterprise)",
          "short": true
        },
        {
          "title": "Category",
          "value": "Outage",
          "short": true
        },
        {
          "title": "Priority",
          "value": "URGENT",
          "short": true
        },
        {
          "title": "Recommended Action",
          "value": "Immediate escalation to on-call engineer",
          "short": false
        }
      ],
      "actions": [
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": "View Ticket",
          "url": "https://support.example.com/tickets/TKT-12345",
          "style": "primary"
        },
        {
          "type": "button",
          "text": "Acknowledge",
          "url": "https://support.example.com/tickets/TKT-12345/acknowledge",
          "style": "danger"
        }
      ],
      "footer": "Support Bot",
      "ts": 1705312800
    }
  ]
}
```

---

AUTHENTICATION HANDLING:
```json
{
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "token_source": "env:SLACK_BOT_TOKEN",
    "header": "Authorization: Bearer {{token}}"
  },
  "headers": {
    "Content-Type": "application/json"
  }
}
```

---

ERROR HANDLING:
```json
{
  "error_responses": {
    "channel_not_found": {
      "slack_error": "channel_not_found",
      "action": "fallback_to_default_channel",
      "fallback_channel": "C0123DEFAULT",
      "retry": true
    },
    "rate_limited": {
      "slack_error": "rate_limited",
      "action": "queue_with_backoff",
      "retry_after": "{{response.headers.Retry-After}}"
    },
    "invalid_auth": {
      "slack_error": "invalid_auth",
      "action": "alert_ops",
      "retry": false
    },
    "message_too_long": {
      "slack_error": "msg_too_long",
      "action": "truncate_and_retry",
      "truncate_field": "attachments[0].text",
      "max_length": 3000
    }
  }
}
```
